DeArrow Integration for uYouEnhanced
=====================================

This integration uses the DeArrow API provided by Ajay Ramachandran.

API LICENSE AND TERMS
---------------------

The DeArrow API (https://sponsor.ajay.app/api/branding) is:
- Free to use for all non-browser extensions
- Does not require an API key
- Subject to the terms at: https://wiki.sponsor.ajay.app/w/API_Docs/DeArrow

DATABASE LICENSE
----------------

The DeArrow database (crowdsourced titles and thumbnails) is licensed under:

Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0 International (CC BY-NC-SA 4.0)
https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/

This means:
- Attribution: You must give appropriate credit to DeArrow/SponsorBlock
- NonCommercial: You may not use the data for commercial purposes
- ShareAlike: If you remix/transform, you must distribute under the same license

ATTRIBUTION
-----------

DeArrow is created by Ajay Ramachandran
- Website: https://dearrow.ajay.app
- GitHub: https://github.com/ajayyy/DeArrow
- API Documentation: https://wiki.sponsor.ajay.app/w/API_Docs/DeArrow

CODE LICENSE
------------

The DeArrow integration code in this directory (Tweaks/DeArrow/) is part of uYouEnhanced
and is provided under the same license as the parent project.

Note: This integration only READS data from the DeArrow API. It does not submit
any data, which would require explicit permission per the API terms.

